headline: Want to Invest in the Nasdaq? This ETF Is a Great Option Heading Into the New Year
summary: When people refer to investing in the Nasdaq, it could mean a few different things.  For some, it means investing in the Nasdaq Composite, one of the U.S. stock market's main three indexes that includes virtually every stock on the Nasdaq (NASDAQ: NDAQ) stock exchange.  For others, it means investing in the Nasdaq-100, a subset of the Nasdaq Composite, tracking the 100 largest non-financial stocks in the index.

headline: Microsoft Just Made a Momentous Decision About Bitcoin That Could Dramatically Affect Your Ability to Become a Crypto Millionaire
summary: On Dec. 10, Microsoft (NASDAQ: MSFT) shareholders voted against a proposal to ask the company to add Bitcoin (CRYPTO: BTC) to its balance sheet. Other high-profile corporations would have surely followed Microsoft's example, leading to a wave of Bitcoin adoption across corporate America.
